"%(appointment_type_name)s: ກະລຸນາຕັ້ງຄ່າ Google Reserve Merchant ຂອງທ່ານສຳລັບ "
"Google Reserve."

#. module: appointment_google_reserve
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/appointment_google_reserve/models/appointment_type.py:0
